                </p>
                <p rend="indent">An orientation session for the new Members of the Board of Visitors
                    was held, in Open Session, in the Lower West Oval Room of the Rotunda on
                    Thursday, <date value="2004-04-15">April 15, 2004</date>, from 10:40 to 11:50
                    a.m. The new Members participating were <name>G. Slaughter Fitz-Hugh,</name>
                    <name>Jr., W. Heywood Fralin,</name>
                    <name>Ms. Glynn D. Key</name> and <name>James W. Head</name>, the Student
                    Member-elect. </p>
                <p rend="indent">The session was conducted by <name>Gordon F. Rainey, Jr.</name>,
                    Rector, President <name>John T. Casteen, III</name>, <name>Leonard W.
                    Sandridge</name>, Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer,
                        <name>Paul J. Forch</name>, General Counsel, and <name>Alexander G. Gilliam,
                        Jr.</name>, Secretary to the Board. </p>
                <p rend="indent"><name>Don R. Pippin</name>, Member of the Board from Wise County,
                    participated. </p>
